WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.160
I once prayed, Lord,

00:00:01.161 --> 00:00:03.061
use me for something great

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:05.900
as mom. As I'm sure that you all can relate,

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.980
our days on this earth are short and few,

00:00:09.080 --> 00:00:12.220
and to give them our all is what we all strive to do.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:16.700
Yet he showed me a great work that seems so small and simple to me.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.020
Loving my children and serving my family.

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:22.740
How can this be? I asked with respect.

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.300
Washing the dishes and doing the clothes.

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:28.240
This isn't something so important that I would have chose.
